profile.bio:
I specialize in leading teams and building the scaffolding that keeps clouds afloat.

I've Founded Thunderbolt Labs, run Product and Engineering at Engine Yard, and co-authored "Rails AntiPatterns: Best Practice Ruby on Rails Refactoring"
